replies.msg:
有樣嘢提多你一次<br />
思源字體由Semibold開始打上嘅weight全部做唔到faux bold，卽係話你而家個網所有用咗&lt;b&gt; tag嘅嘢都冇bold到。<br />
<br />
<img src="https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/181555_7fe70856357281dd6817c967b22b5a5f.png" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F181555_7fe70856357281dd6817c967b22b5a5f.png&h=ae4b5c59&s={SIZE}" /><br />
<br />
<br />
你有兩個解決方法<br />
1, 用Medium唔用Semi Bold<br />
2, 用Bold版整多個subset，然後將個css個頭段改成咁：<br />
<pre><code data-type="">@font-face {
  font-family: &quot;myFont&quot;;
  src: url(&quot;/font/GenYoMinTW-SemiBold-sp1.woff2&quot;) format('woff2');
  font-weight: normal;
}'
@font-face {
  font-family: &quot;myFontbold&quot;;
  src: url(&quot;Bold版新subset嘅位置&quot;) format('woff2');
  font-weight: bold;
}
@font-face {
  font-family: &quot;myFont2&quot;;
  src: url(&quot;/font/GenYoMinTW-SemiBold-7828.woff2&quot;) format('woff2');
  font-weight: normal;
}
b {
  font-family: &quot;myFontbold&quot;;
  font-weight: bold;
}

......</code></pre><br />
<br />
不過一個font都太大，仲加多個font到底著唔著數就自己諗<img src="/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif" class="hkgmoji" />

